    "guidelines": {
        "b&f_guidelines": "BLANC & FISCHER Leadership Principles",
        "act_as_role_models": "We act as role models.",
        "take_responsibility_and_set_goals": "We take ownership and set clear goals.",
        "environment_of_trust": "We create an environment of trust and empowerment.",
        "constructive_feedback": "We provide constructive feedback to develop people.",
        "drive_change": "We drive change.",
        "learn_from_mistakes": "We view mistakes as an opportunity to learn.",
        "support_diversity_and_integration": "We promote diversity and inclusion.",
        "think_and_act_holistic": "We think and act globally.",
        "act_as_role_models_desc": "The leadership of our managers is essential to the success of our business - as managers, we must lead by example. Our colleagues act like our leaders, whether intentionally or not. Credibility is key: we live what we say and mean. That is why the principle of leadership also underpins all the actions of managers and is crucial to the impact of leadership.",
        "take_responsibility_and_set_goals_desc": "In a world of rapid change and diminishing predictability, accountability and decision-making at all levels within the company are essential. We are at the forefront of this.",
        "environment_of_trust_desc": "To reduce the complexity of our work environment and thereby gain competitive strength, we are committed to handing over responsibility properly and trusting in the strengths of our employees. At the same time, we are responsive and predictable to our colleagues.",
        "constructive_feedback_desc": "As a learning organisation, we build on the strengths of our colleagues and seize every opportunity to improve. This can be achieved through regular and timely feedback at individual and organisational level. We promote a positive feedback culture characterised by openness and mutual trust.",
        "drive_change_desc": "In a volatile environment, openness to change, transparency and active design for sustainable change at all levels are guarantees for our survival. That is why our company remains successful in the morning.",
        "learn_from_mistakes_desc": "Speed as a competitive advantage. Developing innovative ideas in ever shorter cycles and learning from potential blowbacks is critical to our company's success. Dealing with failure and the resulting lessons are central to our company's future.",
        "support_diversity_and_integration_desc": "We believe that diversity makes us better and more resilient. Diverse perspectives and critical dialogue at a respectful level lead to more durable solutions and increase our innovative strength.",
        "think_and_act_holistic_desc": "Positioning ourselves as an international group of companies is a decisive competitive advantage. To exploit this advantage, we need to think beyond the boundaries of our own field, collaborate globally and integrate new developments and trends."
    },
